--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Summary
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This software is named ngEO Browse Server, a server providing access to
browse images via WMS. It is developed and maintained by EOX IT Services GmbH,
https://eox.at under contract from the European Space Agency (ESA).

More information is available at <http://ngeo.eox.at>.


